36:30.901 --> 36:32.478
Connections.

36:32.563 --> 36:34.118
That makes you

36:34.203 --> 36:36.804
extremely valuable to me.

36:37.192 --> 36:38.782
Right?

36:39.500 --> 36:41.700
I'm gonna put you
on payroll full-time.

36:41.785 --> 36:44.298
Double what you were
making before.

36:45.076 --> 36:48.290
You got a home right here

36:48.375 --> 36:50.408
with us.

36:51.953 --> 36:54.407
So this ain't
the end of nothing.

36:59.093 --> 37:00.954
It's the beginning.

37:09.618 --> 37:11.418
You want to see?

37:12.181 --> 37:14.478
<i>Nyet, spasibo.</i>

37:14.563 --> 37:15.899
You sure?

37:16.437 --> 37:17.936
Okay.

37:18.515 --> 37:20.774
Do you know what is a "playboy"?

37:23.001 --> 37:25.220
A wealthy man who...

37:25.322 --> 37:28.251
Lives a life
of travel, leisure, women.

37:28.382 --> 37:30.415
Hmm.

37:31.543 --> 37:34.688
We don't even have a word
in Russian for such a man.

37:37.957 --> 37:39.673
- Okay.
- Hmm?

37:39.758 --> 37:41.358
I think we're clear.

37:42.015 --> 37:43.548
Let's go.

38:28.902 --> 38:30.465
Both of you,
hands up in the air!

38:30.600 --> 38:32.967
Slowly, motherfucker!

38:35.290 --> 38:37.113
I know you.

38:37.221 --> 38:38.535
I know you from some...

39:17.597 --> 39:20.137
<i>"Invincible"
by the thompsons playing...</i>

39:33.390 --> 39:34.723
Here's the thing.

39:34.808 --> 39:37.709
Sunday night in almost any
other town in this country,

39:38.031 --> 39:40.031
and everything's closed.

39:40.116 --> 39:41.364
Everyone's asleep in their beds.

39:41.448 --> 39:44.863
Yeah, there's
a lot of hustlers out here, man.

39:46.609 --> 39:48.843
But New York's the city
that never sleeps.

39:49.032 --> 39:50.582
What's Los Angeles?

39:50.667 --> 39:52.600
The city that sleeps in.

39:54.263 --> 39:55.988
Hi, could I get
a coffee, please?

39:56.073 --> 39:58.607
- Sure.
- Thank you. Actually...

39:58.692 --> 40:01.326
Sorry, uh... Do you have pie?

40:01.628 --> 40:03.961
Uh, sure do.
We have apple, pecan,

40:04.046 --> 40:06.146
chocolate cream,
and I think we still have

40:06.231 --> 40:07.535
a piece of BlackBerry cobbler.

40:07.620 --> 40:09.286
- Apple pie would be great.
- Yeah.

40:09.371 --> 40:12.080
Um, could you put
whipped cream on top?

40:12.165 --> 40:14.090
- Sure.
- Thank you.

40:15.190 --> 40:17.224
You're in a good mood.

40:19.143 --> 40:20.832
Yeah, I guess I...

40:20.948 --> 40:22.371
Maybe I am.

40:24.549 --> 40:26.527
Think I owe you an apology.

40:26.676 --> 40:29.213
Or at least an explanation
as to a certain phone call

40:29.298 --> 40:30.899
I may have made yesterday.

40:32.324 --> 40:33.798
A phone call?

40:35.896 --> 40:38.132
Are you talking about
when you threatened to kill me?

40:38.217 --> 40:39.850
Look, I was on drugs, man.

40:39.935 --> 40:41.402
Not in my right mind.

40:41.487 --> 40:43.220
yeah, I heard.

40:44.685 --> 40:47.419
Please tell me that you had,
like, a little bit of fun

40:47.504 --> 40:48.884
before the paranoia kicked in?

40:48.969 --> 40:50.903
Yeah, actually.

40:51.624 --> 40:53.557
The whole family was there.

40:54.517 --> 40:56.131
Everybody happy.

40:56.384 --> 40:57.485
No idea

40:57.570 --> 40:58.989
about the bomb
that was about to drop

40:59.073 --> 41:00.973
- in the middle of it all.
- Yeah.

41:01.058 --> 41:03.892
See, now I'm not sure if you're
talking about the acid or about

41:03.977 --> 41:06.353
me agreeing to do business
with Louie.

41:08.545 --> 41:10.431
Pie will be up in just a minute.

41:10.790 --> 41:12.981
Thanks.

41:19.111 --> 41:21.066
You know, I got to say,

41:21.829 --> 41:23.729
I didn't see that coming.

41:24.027 --> 41:25.504
You should know

41:25.589 --> 41:27.363
that my doing business
with her...

41:28.277 --> 41:30.098
- Not personal...
- Personal?

41:30.744 --> 41:32.270
Just business?

41:33.088 --> 41:34.910
You know how many times
I've used that line?

41:34.995 --> 41:36.207
That's why I'm hoping
you'll understand it.

41:36.291 --> 41:37.051
I mean, shit.

41:37.136 --> 41:38.536
This ain't about me and you,
right?

41:38.621 --> 41:40.287
It's about America,
it's about...

41:40.801 --> 41:42.262
- Winning a war.
- That's right.

41:42.347 --> 41:44.047
And to that point,
I did some thinking

41:44.132 --> 41:45.613
before I came here tonight.

41:46.748 --> 41:48.418
Did you know
in the last three years,

41:48.503 --> 41:50.503
I've made you almost $56 million

41:50.588 --> 41:51.840
to help win that war?

41:51.935 --> 41:54.738
During which time I've been
beaten, shot, imprisoned,

41:54.823 --> 41:56.254
killed people.

41:56.760 --> 41:58.560
Not to mention
unleashing a plague

41:58.645 --> 42:00.356
and selling out my own father.

42:01.089 --> 42:03.490
To keep your gravy train
flowing, of course.

42:03.575 --> 42:04.887
And you wanted it.

42:05.564 --> 42:06.738
Remember?

42:06.823 --> 42:08.289
Yeah, that's true.

42:08.512 --> 42:09.878
And this ain't charity work.

42:09.970 --> 42:12.301
You've taken home some
really nice hazard pay out

42:12.386 --> 42:14.981
- of the whole deal.
- I have. So we are in agreement

42:15.074 --> 42:17.642
that this unlikely partnership
has been more fruitful

42:17.727 --> 42:19.807
and productive than either
of us could have imagined.

42:19.915 --> 42:21.748
We've even had
what I'd like to think were

42:21.833 --> 42:24.066
a few genuine moments
of human connection.

42:24.151 --> 42:26.879
And I do genuinely hope
that you got everything

42:26.964 --> 42:28.465
you wanted out of it,

42:29.196 --> 42:31.530
squeezed every last drop.

42:33.323 --> 42:36.340
'Cause as of this moment,
our partnership is over.

42:40.837 --> 42:43.137
- Anything else I can get for you...?
- We're fine, thank you.

42:43.221 --> 42:44.761
Okay.

42:47.424 --> 42:49.136
Just because
I'm dealing with Louie

42:49.221 --> 42:50.887
does not mean
that you have to quit.

42:50.972 --> 42:52.668
You went behind my back, man.

42:52.753 --> 42:55.787
Undercut me to my biggest
customer, so, yeah, it does.

43:00.856 --> 43:02.481
I've got my money.

43:03.285 --> 43:05.393
Got my lady.

43:05.495 --> 43:07.262
Got a baby on the way.

43:07.926 --> 43:10.051
And I've done my patriotic duty,

43:10.136 --> 43:12.569
then some,
you know that, so I'm out.

43:13.348 --> 43:15.313
And, shit, maybe nobody
will know that a white boy

43:15.686 --> 43:17.543
from Kansas and a black kid
from south central

43:17.628 --> 43:19.928
changed the course
of history forever.

